author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, John Oliver delivered an epically long monologue in defense of quote-unquote “trans women” playing in women's sports. We will dissect his argument in detail. John Oliver is an insufferable, dishonest, intellectual lightweight, and it’s time that someone put him in his place. Also, the Supreme Court says that Trump can continue deporting illegal immigrant gang members. And, there’s a major push now for laws mandating maternity leave. But I think these laws—and the conversation around them–miss the point entirely.
